7:
I'm used to rising early, but not
usually with a sight this pretty to
greet me.
8: Been a while since I got to relax too...
11:
It's weird not having to prep
breakfast.
12:
The hotel staff even handles
cleaning and laundry.
16:
Kinda awesome being treated like
royalty.
35:
You are just. The. Worst. How dare
you leave without saying a word!
36:
Can you imagine how I felt when I
stopped by Starview with a bundle
of premium tea, only to find my two
favorite cuties missing?
39:
I'll tell you! My heart just about broke
in two!
54:
How many... times have I... told you?!
You're gonna suffocate me one of
these days!
63:
I should have done this from the
start.
67:
Come into the darkness, Alky-Walky,
where you can be free of the
accursed light—
76:
You will tempt Alk no further, or I
swear I shall put you down where
you stand!
86:
Oh, you got me good, Light! Is this an
invitation to continue where we last
left off?
94: Fine by me, Wicked Witch of the Rift!
100:
Uhhh... I didn't sign up for an epic
battle when I woke up this morning.
105:
Wait, Belsidia... Is that a swimsuit
you're wearing?
110:
Did you... come here to join us on our
vacation?
115:
I've never been to a resort before,
you know.
116:
I had to take matters into my own
hands when you never invited me.
121:
Alk, don't be deceived by her
innocent act!
127:
Well, Belsidia... You're kind of hard to
track down. We've got no way to
contact you, yeah?
128:
It's not like Stella and I didn't try
looking for you to give you that
invite.
140:
Promise. To make up for it, why don't
we hang out all day today?
145:
Oh, Alky-Walky, you are such a
sweetie!
156:
Okay, enough with the squeezing!
You know where my face goes when
you do that, right?!
167:
A-anyway, we wouldn't purposely
leave a friend out of the fun.
169: Stella and I consider you one of us.
173:
Right... I shouldn't have expected
any less from you two!
182:
I'll see what I can do about
accommodations, okay? There
should be some open rooms left.
185:
*giggle* Aww, don't you want to
share?
193:
...She's actually kind of cute when
she's like this.
198:
What a pure sweetheart. A kid like
him is wasted on you.
203:
Tch! Save your tricks! They won't
work on me!
207: ...Did that sound like a trick to you?
216:
You won't get away with whatever
you're planning! I'll protect Alk from
the darkness until my dying breath!
221:
An idiot through and through... The
world is shrouded in darkness right
now, but it's doing just fine, isn't it?
226: Is this joy I feel? Hahaha!
